{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_15", "eventName": "解離重組", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "15-11", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "一段長夢將醒", "storyInfo": "Friston-3做了一個夢，但奇怪的是可露希爾並沒有為他安裝構造夢境的模組。而剛剛醒來的泡普卡也從舷窗上看到了從未見過的身影。羅德島開始發生異變。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert03_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormlp", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_sand", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弗里斯頓不明白為什麼女兒要約自己在這裡見面。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 50.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_fssand"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡可不算度假的好去處，鞋子裡太容易進沙子。", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，休息一下吧。", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他坐在沙丘上，脫下皮鞋。而傾倒下來的沙塵卻隨風撲向了他的臉，弄得他狼狽不堪。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，咳咳……", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也太不體面了——禮服？我為什麼要穿全套的禮服？", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她為什麼約我來這裡？", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_fssand"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通訊沒有任何回應，他只能在黃沙中茫然地踱步，他呼喚著女兒的名字。"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無人回應他，直到夜色來臨。"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$bar_intro", "key": "$bar_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_desert03_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……派對？", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他循著聲音找了過去，看到了遠處沙丘上張燈結綵的營地。"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他聽到了女兒熟悉的笑聲，他欣喜若狂地狂奔而去。"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還是趕來了我的婚禮，爸爸！", "name": "“女兒”"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那頭金髮讓弗里斯頓幾乎要哭出來。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我找了你很久，我的晨光。", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你的婚禮？", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，典禮快開始了，我們過去吧。", "name": "“女兒”"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會挽著手走過紅毯。祝福我吧，爸爸。", "name": "“女兒”"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弗里斯頓想要牽住她的手，卻怎麼也碰不到。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你不想祝福我嗎？", "name": "“女兒”"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……不……不是這樣……我——", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g8_storage", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_energybody"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）……我——", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你不想祝福我嗎？", "name": "失落的聲音"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）……我的晨光？", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也並不期許我們看到那片真實的星空？", "name": "克麗斯騰"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）……你不是我的晨光。", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）我已經離開了家？這個地下掩體，我記得——", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）“保存間”。", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你不再回應我的請教了嗎？", "name": "克麗斯騰"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）克麗斯騰。你是克麗斯騰……", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）我聽說過你，不不，我見過你……不對，我是從哪裡知道了你？", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）我從沒認識過你——", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_537_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorknob"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）哪個混蛋關上了我的燈？！", "name": "特雷弗·弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）該死！", "name": "弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼要把我關在這裡？", "name": "弗里斯頓"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這又是某種無聊的惡作劇嗎？可露希爾！", "name": "Friston-3"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_rhodesbedroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弗里斯頓發現自己被滿房間的“照片”完全淹沒了，而一本《泰拉全物種詳考》的書冊正蓋在他的鏡頭模組上。"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許也算不上照片……他從未去過照片中的任何地方，也無法去到照片裡的任何地方。"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大量的照片上只印刷著零碎的影像。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沙丘、篝火、營地、金色的頭髮，還有那間暗無天日的保存間。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……夢？", "name": "Friston-3"}, "figure_art": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弗里斯頓做了一個夢。Friston-3做了一個夢。"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而他更是列印了自己的夢。"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我不該有做夢的功能才對，是可露希爾偷偷上傳了新的韌體嗎？", "name": "Friston-3"}, "figure_art": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_rhodesengineeringroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1723_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弗里斯頓先生，我現在沒有時間和你爭論！", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1723_1#11$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以非常明確地向你保證，我絕對絕對沒有給你上傳任何能讓你做夢的韌體。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1723_1#11$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "PRTS的異常越來越嚴重，備用指揮系統上線也還需要時間。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1723_1#11$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……還要手動分配工作內容，我現在眼睛已經快看不過來了！而且某些區域已經完全失去了聯絡，情況完全不明——", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1723_1#11$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放輕鬆，可露希爾。", "name": "Friston-3"}, "figure_art": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不是想要和你爭論，只不過是在嘗試排除引發我身體出現罕見故障的原因。", "name": "Friston-3"}, "figure_art": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們既然已經排除了韌體錯誤和硬體故障的可能性，那——", "name": "Friston-3"}, "figure_art": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "Friston-3"}, "figure_art": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1723_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1723_1#8$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可露希爾，回答我一個很重要的問題……", "name": "Friston-3"}, "figure_art": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "驅動我核心運轉的能源是什麼？", "name": "Friston-3"}, "figure_art": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1723_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，當然是源石。", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1723_1#8$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們的改型作業平台幾乎都是源石驅動？", "name": "Friston-3"}, "figure_art": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1723_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……弗里斯頓先生，你的語氣很可怕。你想說什麼？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1723_1#11$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可露希爾，你是一個天才。", "name": "Friston-3"}, "figure_art": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1723_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1723_1#11$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能想到提前切斷所有改型作業平台與PRTS的連接，但恐怕這遠遠不夠。", "name": "Friston-3"}, "figure_art": "avg_4093_frston_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1723_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？怎麼了？為什麼突然開始顛簸了？", "name": "可露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1723_1#3$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_room_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#2$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "泡普卡是被不斷閃爍的亮光弄醒的。她看向舷窗外，卻並沒有發現任何異樣。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……今天的天氣很好，好像沒有要下雨的樣子。", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是、是其他人在外面訓練弄出來的動靜嗎？", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#8$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦……PRTS的通訊還是沒有恢復嗎？", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#2$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，今天好像是去艦外隔離帶出外勤的日子，先去找梓蘭姐姐報到吧。", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#4$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_rhodesupperdeck", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈囉~大家，都去哪裡了？", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#5$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好安靜啊……梓蘭姐姐現在在哪裡呢？嗯，聯絡不到……", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#2$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_281_popka_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先去餐廳看看吧。", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#2$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "餐廳、餐廳是在這邊——", "name": "泡普卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_281_popka_1#2$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attribut